re where outflows help suppress star\nformation by disturbing rather than expelling the gas and shed light on\npossible ongoing activities in similar quenching galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Aug 2022 16:18:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-26"}
